                                "UNIT V VIBRATION ISOLATION Vibration isolation \u2013 Types of isolation \u2013 Transmissibility \u2013 Passive and active isolation \u2013 Methods of isolation \u2013 Use of springs and damping materials \u2013 Properties of isolating materials \u2013 Vibration control of existing machine foundation"
